{"tid":1301620,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[後續發展] 香港人 請認清抗爭目標","createTime":"2019-07-09T16:41:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-09T18:55:24.000Z","uid":34626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"9a87a54691451725812a76a107957436d023c485","tid":1301620,"uid":34626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T16:41:27.000Z","msg":"宜將剩勇追窮寇。<br />\n<br />\n香港的問題，是系統出了問題，是國柄被中共傀儡操控的問題，只有捍衛香港憲法，普選立法會和特首才能解決。<br />\n<br />\n單一議題逐個去反，你反得幾多次？<br />\n<br />\n香港人時日無多，中共港共三年內會實行社會信用評分制，你的一舉一動都在大數據的監視底下。到時再反已經太遲。因此，這次只許成功不許失敗。失敗了，退無死所，下場就是深圳河以北的地獄鬼國。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭又玩弄以退為進的策略，死硬拒絕五大條件，繼續玩分化拖延的把戲。這個時候最要小心的，是販民共諜代理談判和製造林鄭已經讓步的輿論。<br />\n<br />\n敵退我進，敵疲我打。目標要明確，不是要林鄭再做馬騮戲，落台也無補於事，而是<span style=\"color: red;\">等待美國通過《香港人權與民主法案》，香港普選立法會</span>，整個鬥爭才算成功。<br />\n<br />\n現在形勢才是最凶險之時。在這個關頭鬆懈，下場就是亡國滅種。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/397730460342646/posts/2322022627913410?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F397730460342646%2Fposts%2F2322022627913410%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=aELkmJ%2FgRhSQUMA2B8lhBGqRhi9KU01BjP2Z1UqMPtI%3D&h=62f8b090\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/397730460342646/posts/2322022627913410?sfns=mo</a>"},{"pid":"c82b41df6cd45ffe9351168b9abe8e5852e26852","tid":1301620,"uid":200758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T16:42:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AiR3F8V.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAiR3F8V.jpg&h=f4a2740b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EuDmAd2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEuDmAd2.jpg&h=28455d55&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bf2758b495383837f018c3a9a5c95d5f2f9a1057","tid":1301620,"uid":34626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T16:42:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"980bc1d451fd4305c01abf0501a4bf717fad2c11","tid":1301620,"uid":129068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T16:43:12.000Z","msg":"要政府接納五大訴求"},{"pid":"5a66aa27ff07e03022af80ad3cffb6106dc99fce","tid":1301620,"uid":34626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"980bc1d451fd4305c01abf0501a4bf717fad2c11","tid":1301620,"uid":129068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T16:43:12.000Z","msg":"要政府接納五大訴求"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T16:46:16.000Z","msg":"政府依加就係消耗緊你民意<br />\n<br />\n爭取五大訴求嘅同時<br />\n一定要清楚 最終目標一定係 普選立法會"},{"pid":"4c0ec21a18eb6792307d9faf67fe8727c84932b8","tid":1301620,"uid":34626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T16:48:07.000Z","msg":"輕推"},{"pid":"5b7e6b34fb411d5d41a46c6b3ac5f2270d969520","tid":1301620,"uid":34626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T18:51:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"371714faa2baae313ed57691b4b8c15fc0d64d78","tid":1301620,"uid":263161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T18:55:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}